[[File:Arne_Duncan,_U.S._Secretary_of_Education—Biography,_20090127_DuncanBio.mp4,_0min25sec.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Arne_Duncan,_U.S._Secretary_of_Education—Biography,_20090127_DuncanBio.mp4,_1min03sec.jpg|thumb]]
