他父亲Starkey Duncan是一名[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]的[[心理学|心理学]]教授，他母亲Susan Morton经营着Sue Duncan Children's Center。成长过程中他花了不少业余时间在他母亲的教育中心与那里的教师和学生在一起。他童年的朋友有Ariel Capital Management（现为 Ariel Investments）的[[CEO|CEO]]兼Ariel Community Academy创始人John W. Rogers, Jr.、以及[[伊利诺斯州|伊利诺斯州]]参议员Kwame Raoul、男演员Michael Clarke Duncan、歌手R. Kelly以及[[武术|武术]]获奖者Michelle Gordon。

1987年他获得[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]的[[社会学|社会学]]学士[[拉丁文學位榮譽|拉丁文學位榮譽]]<ref name="Blue Chip Stock">{{cite web |last=Williams |first=Carla D. |url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article.aspx?ref=193164 |title=Blue Chip Stock |publisher=Thecrimson.com |date=1984-01-10 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219190306/http://www.thecrimson.com/article.aspx?ref=193164 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="harvard1">{{cite web |url=http://www.gse.harvard.edu/blog/news_features_releases/2009/09/will-obamas-choice-change-education-in-america.html |title=Will Obama’s Choice Change Education in America? | Harvard Graduate School of Education |publisher=Gse.harvard.edu |date=2010-08-17 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2010-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100125171348/http://www.gse.harvard.edu/blog/news_features_releases/2009/09/will-obamas-choice-change-education-in-america.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

在哈佛上学时，他曾担任多个[[篮球|篮球]]队的领队<ref name="Blue Chip Stock" /><ref>{{cite news | last=Sweet | first=Lynn | title=Arne Duncan to be named Obama Education Secretary | date=December 15, 2008 | publisher=Chicago Sun-Times | url=http://blogs.suntimes.com/sweet/2008/12/arne_duncan_to_be_named_obama.html | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081217032746/http://blogs.suntimes.com/sweet/2008/12/arne_duncan_to_be_named_obama.html | archivedate=2008-12-17}}</ref>。1987到1991年，他是一名专业篮球队运动员，主要是在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]打球，曾效力的球队有[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]的South East Melbourne Magic（[[澳大利亚国家篮球联赛|澳大利亚国家篮球联赛]]的球队之一）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/pm/content/2008/s2448221.htm|title=Former NBL star for White House team|accessdate=2011-12-17|archive-date=2012-06-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68kmONxim?url=http://www.abc.net.au/pm/content/2008/s2448221.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在澳洲他也遇到了他未来的妻子Karen Luann Duncan<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1863062_1863058_1867011,00.html | work=Time | title=Obama | date=December 2, 2008 | accessdate=April 25, 2010 | archive-date=2008-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219201033/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1863062_1863058_1867011,00.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他家居住在[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]的[[阿靈頓縣_(維吉尼亞州)|阿靈頓縣]], 目前两人有正在读[[小学|小学]]的女儿和儿子各一个<ref name="Arne Duncan, U.S. Secretary of Education—Biography]">{{cite web |url=http://www.ed.gov/news/staff/bios/duncan.html |title=Arne Duncan, U.S. Secretary of Education - Biography |publisher=Ed.gov |date= |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615023353/http://www2.ed.gov/news/staff/bios/duncan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

